org.dcm4che2.net
Class State

java.lang.Object
  org.dcm4che2.net.State

public class State
extends Object

Implementation of the DICOM part 8 TCP/IP state machine. This defines the various states that a a TCP/IP connection may be in when a DICOM association is using it.
